snippet.title: SPEED DREAMS - A Racing Day in Melbourne
snippet.description:
Today we are going to release a new track in Speed Dreams. It is a recreation of the famous Albert Park circuit in Melbourne, where the Australian Formula 1 Grand Prix has been held for many years, among many other competitions.

For this we will ride on the back of a MP1 Bavaria FW27, inspired by the 2005 BMW Williams F1 Team car. We hope you like it.

If you want to enjoy this track (and the MP1s) you can download the first beta of our next version 2.3.0. You have more info in this news in our official website:
https://www.speed-dreams.net/en/new-2-3-0-beta-1-release/

You can find this game and more info about this Open Source project on:
https://www.speed-dreams.net 

Music by:
Killing Time Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
